title: I KILL PXLS - 2008 - Press Start
description:
This is the first album from I KILL PXLS called "Press Start". I&#039;m releasing it for free so feel free to share it around however you want.

The music itself is electro inspired by video game culture in general. Influences include MSTRKRFT, Justice, Mr Oizo, Andre 3000, TV on the Radio, Yuzo Koshiro, Tepr, and way more that I don&#039;t feel like listing now.

If you want to check out some more of my music, check out my official site at:
www.ikillpxls.com


Or my myspaces at:

I&#039;m also taking donations on the front page of my official site if you want to contribute. So download and listen (it&#039;s free damnit!) and enjoy. Thanks!

-Marques/I KILL PXLS-
